14
00:01:20,519 --> 00:01:21,379
Honey.

15
00:01:22,280 --> 00:01:23,180
Honey.

16
00:01:24,739 --> 00:01:25,719
Honey.

17
00:01:30,500 --> 00:01:31,060
It's okay.

18
00:01:31,379 --> 00:01:31,980
It's okay.

19
00:01:33,060 --> 00:01:34,140
Just a nightmare.

20
00:01:34,900 --> 00:01:36,000
I visited Dad today.

21
00:01:36,579 --> 00:01:37,340
He's fine.

22
00:01:38,219 --> 00:01:38,579
No.

23
00:01:38,900 --> 00:01:39,420
No.

24
00:01:40,099 --> 00:01:41,500
