33
00:02:11,500 --> 00:02:12,060
(It's bad.)

34
00:02:12,340 --> 00:02:13,900
(He suspects I can see.)

35
00:02:14,300 --> 00:02:15,620
(I can't let him find out.)

36
00:02:16,020 --> 00:02:16,620
Honey.

37
00:02:20,099 --> 00:02:21,099
Why do you smell

38
00:02:21,099 --> 00:02:22,159
