40
00:02:29,659 --> 00:02:30,199
Honey.

41
00:02:30,199 --> 00:02:30,919
Really?

42
00:02:31,939 --> 00:02:32,479
Yes.

43
00:02:32,900 --> 00:02:34,560
How could there be women's perfume?

44
00:02:43,560 --> 00:02:45,120
