53
00:03:04,439 --> 00:03:06,199
Don't be so mean.

54
00:03:09,219 --> 00:03:10,740
(She can still laugh?)

55
00:03:11,659 --> 00:03:13,000
(It proves her eyes)

56
00:03:13,840 --> 00:03:15,219
(haven't recovered.)

57
00:03:16,199 --> 00:03:16,919
(Ye Dong,)

58
00:03:17,479 --> 00:03:18,680
(you monster.)

59
00:03:19,280 --> 00:03:21,039
(I want to tear you apart.)

60
00:03:21,740 --> 00:03:22,979
(I was blind.)

61
00:03:23,099 --> 00:03:24,139
(I let the wolf in.)

62
00:03:24,620 --> 00:03:26,500
(I killed Dad.)

63
00:03:28,840 --> 00:03:29,500
Who?

64
00:03:30,199 --> 00:03:31,280
Who's shouting?

65
00:03:33,740 --> 00:03:34,379
Ms. Lin,

66
00:03:34,780 --> 00:03:35,919
