67
00:03:36,620 --> 00:03:37,879
Here to deliver documents.

68
00:03:40,819 --> 00:03:41,539
Are you okay?

69
00:03:42,500 --> 00:03:42,800
Y...

70
00:03:43,199 --> 00:03:44,020
Yes.

71
00:03:46,460 --> 00:03:47,180
Dong,

72
00:03:47,900 --> 00:03:48,879
there's an old mutt

73
00:03:49,099 --> 00:03:50,280
dead in the basement.

74
00:03:50,539 --> 00:03:51,680
Go dispose of it.

75
00:03:53,819 --> 00:03:54,400
Mom,

76
00:03:55,139 --> 00:03:57,080
since when do we have an old dog?

77
00:03:58,699 --> 00:04:00,740
Some stray crawled into the basement.

78
00:04:05,360 --> 00:04:05,960
Honey.

79
00:04:06,639 --> 00:04:07,060
Quick.

80
00:04:07,319 --> 00:04:08,120
Go help Mom.

81
00:04:08,439 --> 00:04:09,199
Help her out.

82
00:04:10,219 --> 00:04:10,819
Mr. Ye,

83
00:04:10,939 --> 00:04:11,539
Ms. Lin,

84
00:04:11,800 --> 00:04:13,060
if there's nothing else,

85
00:04:13,280 --> 00:04:14,400
I'll take my leave.

86
00:04:15,319 --> 00:04:16,079
Wait.

87
00:04:20,500 --> 00:04:21,279
Mr. Ye,

88
00:04:21,459 --> 00:04:23,120
any other orders?

89
00:04:24,699 --> 00:04:25,360
Yufei,

90
00:04:25,899 --> 00:04:26,920
since you're here,

91
00:04:27,240 --> 00:04:28,120
do me a favor.

92
00:04:28,579 --> 00:04:29,399
Lend a hand.

93
00:04:30,579 --> 00:04:31,279
Mr. Ye,

94
00:04:31,959 --> 00:04:33,000
I'm scared of dogs.

95
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:34,139
It's just a dead dog.

96
00:04:34,519 --> 00:04:35,579
Nothing to fear.

97
00:04:36,980 --> 00:04:37,459
Come.

98
00:04:43,579 --> 00:04:44,220
Honey,

99
00:04:44,779 --> 00:04:45,459
stay here

100
00:04:45,500 --> 00:04:46,019
and rest.

101
00:04:46,279 --> 00:04:47,339
I'll be right back.

102
00:05:11,339 --> 00:05:12,079
Honey.

103
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:22,600
What's wrong,

104
00:05:23,240 --> 00:05:23,980
honey?

105
00:05:35,060 --> 00:05:35,980
Come with me.

106
00:05:41,699 --> 00:05:42,420
Honey,

107
00:05:43,720 --> 00:05:44,740
is anything wrong?

108
00:05:53,060 --> 00:05:54,279
Just come with me.

109
00:06:09,259 --> 00:06:10,319
It's all sorted out.

110
00:06:10,579 --> 00:06:11,560
Come in and help.

111
00:06:12,060 --> 00:06:12,600
Lady,

112
00:06:12,699 --> 00:06:13,319
