130
00:07:21,740 --> 00:07:22,480
It's nothing.

131
00:07:23,019 --> 00:07:23,720
I'm fine.

132
00:07:24,019 --> 00:07:26,079
I'll cook you something nutritious later

133
00:07:26,339 --> 00:07:27,439
