145
00:08:23,899 --> 00:08:24,959
Wait here for me.

146
00:08:25,540 --> 00:08:26,800
I'll be right back.

147
00:09:31,220 --> 00:09:32,000
Baba.

148
00:09:32,419 --> 00:09:33,039
